{"id": "1280453160351305740", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176198078026498098", "author_name": "huangyu0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "主要是王的機制已經固化，目前最高難度也跟滿練角色有差距，玩家的互動性又全靠玩家自主的討論跟自我限制（二回殺等等）", "timestamp": "2024-09-03T09:03:43.097000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1280453782727032833", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176198078026498098", "author_name": "huangyu0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "我個人認為可以出一個新模式，王不要放血量並且依照回合變強（多段超過血量的攻擊絕對能有效抑制回合數），用這個來得到排名（根據最高傷害，生存回合來評分）", "timestamp": "2024-09-03T09:06:11.483000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
